title: Beaver Banter podcast discusses quarterbacks, Colorado: Oregon State rundown
text:
On the latest edition of The Oregonian's Beaver Banter podcast, Oregon State reporters Gina Mizell and Danny Moran discuss the new twist in the Beavers' quarterback competition and preview Saturday's contest against Colorado.
You can listen in the player below or subscribe on iTunes by searching "Beaver Banter." Submit questions, bold predictions and over/under categories on Twitter to @ginamizell and @DannyJMoran.
